			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>The delicate metalwork in this belt is unmistakably magical, as is the feeling that courses through you when you lash it on.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Waist Slot</b><b>:</b> Rare</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain a +2 bonus to Diplomacy checks and Intimidate checks against dwarves.</li>\n<li>You can speak, read, and write Dwarven.</li>\n</ul></p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Encounter (Immediate Interrupt)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> An attack pushes, pulls, or slides you.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> You ignore 1 square of the forced movement.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Immediate Reaction)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You take ongoing poison damage from an attack.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> You can make a saving throw against the ongoing poison damage.</p>",
